{"tid":1321633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【報夢教路】新城市事件分析+投訴搵最大嗰個幾個","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T08:02:42.000Z","uid":56037,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6209b979ad77fdbaaa5996dc6cd41b6354abb06d","tid":1321633,"uid":56037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見朋友，難得佢心水咁清，我瞓醒又記得到，同大家分享下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POczexx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOczexx.png&h=d594a396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 新城市請親都係後生，呢啲老矮騎呢，肚腩大大嘅，又會係佢地員工啦。係乜人，大家心照。咁早喬裝去新城市做乜？梗係視察環境，準備夜晚圍打啦。官商勾結啊呢啲叫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4NjqE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4NjqE1.png&h=ffa7fb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 著晒制服明張目膽帶路，都夠膽死出聲明話無俾啲狗入商場，你話呢班友幾賤呢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUZYGd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUZYGd5.png&h=577c341c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 嗱，商場有權唔俾閉路電視紀錄啲狗架，你睇吓PP就知，咁把炮咪向法庭申請囉。嗱，最終有無俾我就唔知，但按常理推斷，高層話唔俾，落乜鬼控制室吖。係無俾班狗入商場嘅，我唔信會俾閉路電視紀錄囉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HHE9NWc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHHE9NWc.png&h=8e8e1e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 投訴要知架步。新城市商業大廈，六樓辦公室，唔係四樓櫃面啊。朋友俾埋資料我，大家核對吓。<br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場推廣部<br />\n高級推廣經理 <br />\nMs Sheila Chan<br />\nTel: 2606 1720<br />\nemail : sheilachan@shkp.com <br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場租務部 <br />\n助理總經理許嘉雯 Ms Yoki Hui, <br />\nTel: 2828 7754<br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場1期物業管理處<br />\nDeputy general manager <br />\nBen Kam 2609 3601<br />\n<br />\nManager <br />\nFiona Chan 2609 3641 <br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場1期物業管理處 office general line  2609 3638"},{"pid":"97a7d7622f818ef01bab2d2781dfaa1667222842","tid":1321633,"uid":56037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd178a03c63bbaf933f93354d10d3bf018cb733","tid":1321633,"uid":56037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64b7bf4d66d2d2640613722906486d4cef4afe1","tid":1321633,"uid":56037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a7f0879e21dddce2a30a724af45f1dbc4f3d7f","tid":1321633,"uid":56037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e657fec27c65bd61ac9af7b95865a137158d43f0","tid":1321633,"uid":56037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa802fc8dcca3ab69e580f63c490b110fe3d07c","tid":1321633,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f469c5e92c77179dee22657e29decc21e2296574","tid":1321633,"uid":56037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa802fc8dcca3ab69e580f63c490b110fe3d07c","tid":1321633,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17